Class Dictionary

java.lang.Object
Dictionary
public class Dictionary
extends java.lang.Object
The dictionary class, containing the binary search tree with all the words. Each dictionary is a one way mapping from a language to another language and doesn't work the other way. It contains methods from translating words and phrases. Alongside the binary tree with the collection of phrases it also contains a list of all verb suffixes and prefixes.

    • translateVerb

      public java.lang.String translateVerb​(java.lang.String phrase)
      Trims the phrase of all verb suffixes and then tries to translate it. Returns the translation or null if no translation exists. Using this we can translate even conjugated verbs (walked, drowned) while only havign a record of their infinitives (walk, drown).
      Parameters:

      Returns:
      String
